@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### Get all events
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events

### Get event by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/1

### Get non-existent event (should return 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/999

### Create a new event
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "DevOps Days Munich",
  "date": "2026-10-05",
  "city": "Munich",
  "description": "DevOps community conference"
}

### Update an event
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/events/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "TechConf 2026 - Updated",
  "date": "2026-09-16",
  "city": "Munich",
  "description": "Updated description"
}

### Delete an event
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/events/3
